<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-54-0902 </DOCNO><TEXT>A short history is given of the development of a lightning location systembased on a network of direction finding stations. The system makes useof the earth-ionosphere waveguide to greatly reduce the effect of anomalouswaves on bearing accuracy. An improved direction finding loop antennais described. Details of the system performance are given.</TEXT></DOC>